description:
Would you like to learn how to grow your faith? Do you struggle with thoughts that God hasn’t forgiven you, doesn’t care about your problems, or doesn’t hear you? In this episode, Pastor Pavel Goia addresses the problems Christians face with belief. He reminds us that our daily problems are not the real problem. Our real problem is our lack of faith. Satan uses our problems to destroy our faith, to make us distrust God, to take away our belief. With stories of how others overcame their unbelief and the amazing results that followed, Pastor Goia shows how to grow your faith, how to learn to trust God, how to truly believe.  

What are the symptoms that we’re lacking faith? How can we know if we’re abiding in Christ? Why don’t we trust God more than we do? What is the secret to developing strong faith?  How do we fix our belief problems? Find out in this inspiring, belief-building presentation.

#PavelGoia #AmazingDiscoveries #GrowingInChrist #Sabbath
